            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Quintum in hac tabula depon<supplied reason="lost">o</supplied> aversum <lb n="2"/>se suisque rationibus vitaeque male consum<lb break="no" n="3"/>mantem ita uti galli bellonarive absciderunt concide<lb break="no" n="4"/>runtve se sic illi abscissa sit fides fama faculit<supplied reason="lost">a</supplied>s nec illi <lb n="5"/>in numero hominum sunt neque ille sit q<supplied reason="lost">u</supplied>omodi <note>sic</note> et ille <lb n="6"/>mihi fraudem fecit sic illi sancta Mater Magn<supplied reason="lost">a</supplied> et relegis<supplied reason="lost">ti</supplied> <lb n="7"/>cuncta ita uti arbor siccabit se in sancto sic et illi siccet <lb n="8"/>fama fides fortuna faculitas tibi commendo Attihi <note>sic</note> d&amp;lt;o&amp;gt;mine <lb n="9"/>ut me vindices ab eo ut intra annum vertente<supplied reason="lost">m</supplied><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> exitum <lb n="10"/>illius vilem malum
            </ab></div>
